name: Cicerone
tagline: An simple interpreter to learn basis of programming , open source & completely  free
body:
### Welcome to Cicerone project.

### Goal
Born for a good exam result, now it wants be a open source project to improve programming quality and ability of younger programmers.
More description come fastly.

### More to do!
Now starts , how we will arrive ? 

### Authors and Contributors
We are three sadly boys that, to do a work project for our university, we create this interpreter .

### Support or Contact
Use email support,it's open but not a real work , if you want please donate with paypal account  "asetyde4@hotmail.com".
Many Thanks
